鄧萃雯外，只有黎耀祥、謝雪心和敖嘉年有得留低，更多詳情有待公布。至於其他「余黨」的去向，久久未有新劇的黃翠如，日前已正式續約，正等待公司安排工作，而洪永城則於稍後會在另一套新劇擔正。<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210414/458854191780073472543168.jpeg/VcI1VmE4uBFe56MfxLXA_dZhVv-HbH52KP0BZyj9AWc?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210414%2F458854191780073472543168.jpeg%2FVcI1VmE4uBFe56MfxLXA_dZhVv-HbH52KP0BZyj9AWc%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=416f1cc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:41:14.000Z","msg":"成班老野做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e66632056a9330126277310b377389f56fcb585","tid":2487773,"uid":24311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c264fee591ec0486ee5c1b564be997c05e91b549","tid":2487773,"uid":206002,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T23:16:24.000Z","msg":"個劇名呃到啲廢老廢中睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外想講tvb編劇作劇名好老尷<br />\n條友作完有冇打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無中二病完全係作唔出嚟 咩衰神咩不要臉 幼稚園學生思路都正常過班編劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多大陸漫畫名都係咁上下<br />\n分分鐘txb嗰班都係大陸人"},{"pid":"f8078c52936abc519562c4af4ba67ef427c57918","tid":2487773,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"657450bddde142aa4d2f00dc11187bccf794d892","tid":2487773,"uid":83328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81bb629e5fbf6649d9165dec30000b2b131a3c93","tid":2487773,"uid":103230,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:05:44.000Z","msg":"咁多老野點解唔索性做大戲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:46:55.000Z","msg":"每年都有一獲啦, 歡樂滿東華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cla